description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Patient Contact Advisor - be part of a high performing team who make a daily difference to patients!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Solent have a great opportunity for you to join our Single Point of Access (SPA) team based at the Royal South Hants Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SPA is the gateway and first point of contact for Patients and Health Care Professionals for a variety of services across the Southampton and Portsmouth area. These services cover our community nursing, physio and occupational therapy teams as well as sexual health, palliative care and podiatry teams.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work as part of an established and dynamic team providing primarily a telephone service including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;appointment management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;patient account management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;referral management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;waiting list management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;other administrative duties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, flexible, reliable and self-motivated person with excellent communication skills and who has the ability to work both within a team and directly unsupervised. Whilst previous call centre experience is not essential you need to be comfortable working to a daily monitored standards of quality and accuracy. Full training will be provided.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SPA is open 7 days per week from 8am to 8pm, including all bank holidays. The successful applicant will be included in the roster to work a combination of early, late and weekend shifts some of which will be eligible for enhanced shift pay rates.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel this is the opportunity for you and you are prepared to be a hard-working, effective flexible team player and share our team behaviors then we look forward to your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Single Point of Access&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our behaviors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Approachable &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supportive &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible—Adapt/agile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Thoughtful -Stop &amp; think&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fairness &amp; Equality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Positive &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calm&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information, please contact Jayne Williams - SPA Service Manager on jayne.williams@solent.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that should this post attract sufficient interest, we may choose to close at an earlier date. We strongly suggest that you apply at an early stage.&lt;strong&gt; If we have not contacted you within four weeks of the closing date of this post, please presume that you have not been selected.&lt;/strong&gt; Candidates selected for interview will be contacted within 2-3 weeks; therefore you should check your emails regularly including junk mail folders.&lt;/p&gt;
